&lt;h2&gt;Features&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;features&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#features&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Powerful Virtualization&lt;/strong&gt; ‚Äì ProxLink leverages Proxmox VE&amp;rsquo;s intuitive web interface to efficiently manage virtual machines and containers, ensuring flexibility and scalability.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Robust Network Security&lt;/strong&gt; ‚Äì The lab integrates pfSense firewall/router capabilities, delivering advanced security features, VPN connectivity, and comprehensive network monitoring.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Seamless Remote Access&lt;/strong&gt; ‚Äì TailScale provides secure, reliable remote connectivity within the lab environment, with minimal setup and low-maintenance operation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Reliable Storage Management&lt;/strong&gt; ‚Äì TrueNAS is used for data organization, advanced snapshotting, redundancy, and secure file-sharing, enhancing overall data resilience. (In-Progress)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Extensible and Customizable&lt;/strong&gt; ‚Äì ProxLink offers extensibility through scripting, automation, thorough documentation, and powerful integrations, allowing flexible customization.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Optimized for Learning and Growth&lt;/strong&gt; ‚Äì The project is structured to provide a practical, accessible learning environment suitable for all skill levels, from beginners to experienced IT professionals.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Questions or Feedback?&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;questions-or-feedback&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
